INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(157,'Luxor: Quest for the Afterlife','Luxor Quest: For The Afterlife, blasts onto the Silk Road in search of riches beyond imagination. One of the most beautiful and well - known faces in history is also one of its greatest mysteries. When the sacred artifacts of Queen Nefertiti are stolen, her earth-bound spirit calls upon you to find them so her eternal spirit will rise. Wielding the falcon-winged shooter of Horus, you choose your own paths on an expansive journey out of Egypt. In your quest to reveal and assemble Queen Nefertitis artifact pieces, youll explore exotic Persia, Syria, India and other regions of the Near East. Track down each of the robbers and defeat them in an all-new Battle Mode. A great adventure awaits in, Luxor Quest: For The Afterlife!','3DS','3DS','Jun 29, 2012',NULL,'http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/668994-luxor-quest-for-the-afterlife');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(158,'Cocoto: Alien Brick Breaker','Cocoto renews an arcade game classic! The devilish Cocoto is back in an incredibly addictive game, brilliantly renewing the great brick breaker classic! Travel through the 5 planets of Cocotos universe to protect them from alien fire by firing back their projectiles with your magic shield. Progress through the game confronting waves of more and more enemies with increasingly amusing weapons, and unlock new powers for your shield.','3DS','3DS','Jan 24, 2013','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/701099-cocoto-alien-brick-breaker');
