INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(308,'Horrid Henry: The Good, The Bad and The Bugly','Greetings one and all, Horrid Henry herein glorious 3D! Now we all know how much of a smelly nappy baby my wormy worm little brother is. Only now hes only gone and lost his precious Bunny again and guess whos getting gonna get the blame? Me of course!! So our mission, Purple Hand Gang Members, is to find that Bunny, and I need you to help me! So get ready, cos were gonna have loads of fun doing it!','3DS','3DS','Nov 25, 2011',NULL,'http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/643862-horrid-henry-the-good-the-bad-and-the-bugly');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(309,'Hitori by Nikoli','With the Nikoli puzzle series, you can enjoy high-quality "Sudoku" puzzles, created by Nikoli, who gave the world-famous puzzle its name. The Nintendo 3DS allows for the realization of simple and easy to play operability. "Hitori by Nikoli" contains 50 sudoku puzzles. "Hitori" is a puzzle in which you fill in any unnecessary numbers, making sure that the same number doesnt appear twice in the same line. Once you get the hang of it, you can feel the joy of figuring out the many various gimmicks thought up by the creator. This is a puzzle for real connoisseurs. To ensure your long-term enjoyment, were prepared both a "Stage Clear" mode and a "Random" mode. In "Stage Clear" mode, you progress by clearing puzzles one by one, and in "Random" mode puzzles are generated at random. Please enjoy this high-quality "Hitori" game.','3DS','3DS','Sep 27, 2012','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/647280-hitori-by-nikoli');
