INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(474,'Cloudy With a Chance of Meatballs 2','Following the events of Sony Pictures Animations original culinary comedy, Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs 2 continues the exciting journey of inventor Flint Lockwood and his friends as they rush to save the world from his most infamous machine that is now creating food-animal hybrids- "Foodimals"! This action-adventure title, starring a dazzling cast of characters, art, and environments from the animated feature, is ideal for young gamers and fans of the film of all ages. Complete with a suite of unlockable levels, unique character abilities and power-ups, and bonus Challenge and Survival gameplay modes in addition to the main story, Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs 2 is a game youll savor with every play.','3DS','3DS','Sep 17, 2013','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/724205-cloudy-with-a-chance-of-meatballs-2');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(475,'Best of Arcade Games: Bubble Buster','Rediscover a timeless puzzle game with Bubble Buster! Solve 50 puzzles in Adventure mode, and play any level you want in Free mode. Precise aim, wildcard bubbles... unlock lots of bonuses using the points you accumulate while playing. Take on obstacles such as magic bubbles that change colour!','3DS','3DS','Aug 13, 2015','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/126523-best-of-arcade-games-bubble-buster');
