INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(615,'Sweet Memories Blackjack','Sweet Memories Blackjack is a card game that allows you to play blackjack with a number of different girls. These Japanese high school girls are both cute and sweet additions to the poker club youve created. One day, an old neighbor name Kasumi enrolled at your school, after moving back to the city. Your parents are acquaintances, so she gained the approval of staying at your home during enrollment. You have sweet childhood memories of the time spent with her. Simply face your friend, and the memories will return. The time you spend playing blackjack together, increases the connection between the two of you, and you will find out that she is the perfect match for you.','3DS','3DS','Jul 12, 2012','T','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/672442-sweet-memories-blackjack');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(616,'Kodomo ni Anshin Shite Ataerareru Game Series: Sekai Meisaku Douwa - Oyako de Yomeru Game Ehon Bouken-Hen','Kodomo ni Anshin Shite Ataerareru Game Series: Sekai Meisaku Douwa - Oyako de Yomeru Game Ehon Bouken-Hen is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Alchemist, which was released in Japan in 2013.','3DS','3DS','Nov 28, 2013',NULL,'http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/732628-kodomo-ni-anshin-shite-ataerareru-game-series');
