INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(745,'Senran Kagura: Shoujotachi no Shinei','Asuka, Ikaruga, Katsuragi, Yagyuu and Hibari are five novice ninjas with different powers, but all of them have one aim, to rid the world of evil. Take the girls in a horizontal scrolling action adventure, slash at the obstacles that block their way and combo enemies in the air. When gamers execute a move beautifully or satisfy some other challenging conditions, the girls will reward them with special cut scenes full of fan-service moments. The fast pace fights will appeal to action fans while the bishojo lovers can enjoy the cut scenes. But dont skip the story, as the scenarios are written by Kitashima Yukinori of 428 Fuusa sareta shibuya fame.','3DS','3DS','Sep 22, 2011',NULL,'http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/627123-senran-kagura-shoujotachi-no-shinei');
