INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(763,'DreamWorks Madagascar 3 & The Croods: Combo Pack','2 full games for one low price. This combo pack contains the full versions of both Madagascar 3: The Video Game and The Croods: Prehistoric Party. It is loaded with action and adventure featuring your favorite DreamWorks Animation characters and is sure to provide hours of fun for kids of all ages. In Madagascar 3: The Video Game, adventure across Europe as Alex the Lion, Marty the Zebra, Gloria the Hippo and Melman the Giraffe while you find a way home under the perfect cover: a traveling circus. The Croods: Prehistoric Party. combines the ultimate fun of a family party game with Croods style action as you journey through 30 unique and addictive mini games.','3DS','3DS','Mar 25, 2014','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/739432-dreamworks-madagascar-3-and-the-croods-combo-pack');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(764,'Real Heroes: Firefighter 3D','In this first-person fire & rescue action game players will enter the soot-stained boots of an everyday hero as a newly graduated academy cadet getting their start in a big city fire station. Players must use the tools of the trade like the axe, hose and saw to battle raging blazes, tackle explosive environments and rescue survivors.','3DS','3DS','Aug 10, 2012','E10+','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/675600-real-heroes-firefighter-3d');
