INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1021,'Disney Infinity: Toy Box Challenge','In Disneys most ambitious video game initiative ever, Disney Infinity introduces an all-new game universe where a spark of imagination unlocks a fantastical world where players have unprecedented freedom and endless opportunity to create stories and play experiences starring the beloved characters from Walt Disney and Pixar Animation Studios most popular franchises.','3DS','3DS','Aug 18, 2013','E10+','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/699796-disney-infinity-toy-box-challenge');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1022,'Dream Trigger 3D','Dream Trigger 3D showcases the wow factor of the 3DS like no other game. A stunning mixture of explosive graphics and nonstop action, it is a signature shooter for the system. Play as a fixer of dreams, turning nightmare landscapes into gorgeous dreamscapes in this must-have visual masterpiece for new 3DS owners.','3DS','3DS','May 10, 2011','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/619024-dream-trigger-3d');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1023,'Puzzler Brain Games','Puzzler Brain Games is a completely new franchise presented by Puzzler, the worlds largest provider of puzzle content, and developed by the same team behind the multimillion selling Puzzler World series. An all new game that brings exciting timed challenges in the form of Visual, Word, Mathematical and Memory puzzles for young and old alike to enjoy.','3DS','3DS','Apr 19, 2013',NULL,'http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/697070-puzzler-brain-games');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1024,'Best of Arcade Games: Tetraminos','Rediscover a timeless puzzle classic with Tetraminos! Become a Tetraminos pro over 50 levels of increasing difficulty. Find the best place for your pieces, and eliminate as many lines as possible in one go. Earn points to unlock bonuses that can be used at any time: bombs, piece storage... Discover the new Real Gravity game mode, and build the highest Tetraminos tower possible before it collapses!','3DS','3DS','Aug  6, 2015','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/3ds/126524-best-of-arcade-games-tetraminos');
