INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1169,'Asphalt 7: Heat','Hit the speed of heat in the newest, fastest, most visually stunning edition of the famed Asphalt series.A FIRST-CLASS LINEUPDrive 60 different cars from the worldâs most prestigious manufacturers, like Ferrari, Lamborghini and Aston Martin, including the legendary DeLorean.RACE ACROSS THE GLOBEGear up to race on 15 tracks set in real cities around the world, including brand new tracks in Hawaii, Paris, London, Miami and Rio.CHALLENGE THE WORLDThe completely revamped multiplayer lets you take on up to 5 of your friends locally or online. Keep track of whoâs the best with the new Asphalt Tracker that lets you compare stats, show off achievements and challenge rivals. You can also find new online opponents with the matchmaking system. Practice hard, because there are special events that will pit you against the best in the world! YOUR WAY OR THE HIGHWAYPlay however you please with 6 different game modes packed with 15 leagues and 150 different races.CUTTING EDGE GRAPHICS Every car and track is more beautiful than ever thanks to graphics that push the limits of your device and the Retina display.A RECORD OF SUCCESSAcclaimed by both media and players, the Asphalt license has already attracted several million players worldwide... Come and join the ride! ----Visit our official site at http://www.gameloft.comFollow us on Twitter at http://twitter.com/gameloft or like us on Facebook at http://facebook.com/gameloft to get more info about all our upcoming titles.Check out our videos and game trailers on www.youtube.com/gameloft. Discover our blog at http://blog.gameloft.com/ for the inside scoop on everything Gameloft.','Android','Android','Jun 21, 2012',NULL,'http://www.gamefaqs.com/android/674951-asphalt-7-heat');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1170,'Final Fantasy IV','"FINAL FANTASY IV" has finally come to the Android! The title first debuted in 1991 as the fourth installment in the FINAL FANTASY series. Wildly popular thanks to its unique characters and dramatic storylines, it went on to be ported to many different platforms. FINAL FANTASY IV was the first title to introduce the Active Time Battle (ATB) system, which has become synonymous with the series. It also saw the introduction of the Augment system, which enabled the transfer of abilities from other characters and gave players an edge in battles. This iconic title is packed with other amazing features. - Voice acting for event scenes Key events unfold with spoken dialogue. - Deeply emotional portrayals Characters go through visibly apparent emotional changes. - A brand new mapping feature Players start with a completely blank dungeons map, adding an element of the unknown to the mix! - Jukebox Players can listen to the games music anytime they want.','Android','Android','Jun  3, 2013',NULL,'http://www.gamefaqs.com/android/695717-final-fantasy-iv');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1171,'Blood Brothers','===========================================================================A special promotion is running!Get Road Knight, a rare card, and 2 Mandrakes FREE for a limited time until September 7th!SPONSORED BY APPODAY (SAVE $4.99)Download Appoday to get more premium games like Blood Brothers for free.**Collect your rewards in Wagon after completing the tutorial!**==========================================================================To celebrate the release of the iOS version, new players will receive a rare dragon card as a login bonus!Thrilling battles! Mysterious characters! Secrets to be discovered! Experience Blood Brothers now on iOS!Blood Brothers is a dark fantasy game; an epic world of knights, elves, goblins and vampires ready to battle!The tale of a hero turned vampire, who must bind an army in a pact of blood in order to exact vengeance on a corrupt empire. Choose one of eight heroes - knight, samurai, high elf, dark elf, ape, lizardman, dwarf, or goblin - to lead your army to victory!Killer battles! Mysterious characters! Secrets to be discovered!Experience Blood Brothers now on iOS!REVIEWS? “One of the most accomplished of the rather strange RPG-Pokemon-Tamagotchi hybrid breeds that have started to multiply on the app stores in recent months, Blood Brothers will keep you busy in snatches for some time to come.” – modojo.comFeatures-Wield skills from archery to sorcery, lightning to fire!-Customize your party to gain a strategic edge!-Bond characters together in dark rites!-Evolve characters to boost their strength!-Traverse villages, castles, dungeons, and more!-New characters and areas in free updates!Explore the endless world of Blood Brothers.WHAT OTHER USERS ARE SAYING:? “Love this game! It has a whole new concept on the RPG games out there. If you like Rage of Bahamut or other card RPGs you will love this--it doesn’t use the card concept, which I love.”? “This game is a blast! It’s like a very interactive strategic board game and so far the best RPG game Ive played on my phone.”? “If you like any kind of CCG you will love this game.”*? “Very fun and addicting. If you are a fan of games like Rage of Bahamut where you collect and evolve, you should definitely check it out.”TIPS FROM OTHER USERS? “Use a defensive formation when leveling new familiars, leave higher level familiars in the front.”? “Take short or long paths in zones based on how many battles you want.”? “Special events come often and you should participate (even low levels).”The world of Blood Brothers knows no bounds!Blood Brothers is powered by Mobage, the best, free, social game network.','Android','Android','Aug 13, 2012',NULL,'http://www.gamefaqs.com/android/681656-blood-brothers');
