INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1608,'Sonic Shuffle','Illumina, the Guardian Angel, needs your help. The mysterious monster Void has locked up the power of the Precioustones, and its up to you to guide Sonic and his friends through incredible game boards to recover them. Play with up to 3 friends to find out who will be the first to save the land of Maginaryworld. Play minigames, fight bosses, work your way through special events, and more, in Sonics latest adventure!','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Nov 13, 2000','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/256050-sonic-shuffle');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1609,'Marvel vs. Capcom','Imagine the battle: Spider-Man vs. Mega Man... Incredible! Or, who would stand victorious in Strider vs. Captain America? Amazing! Now Capcom brings this #1 smash arcade fantasy fighter to the Sega Dreamcast! Experience the worlds most insane battles between your favorite legenedary Capcom characters and Super Heroes of the Marvel Universe.','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Sep 30, 1999','T','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/197868-marvel-vs-capcom');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1610,'Army Men: Sarge''s Heroes','As Sarge, you must rescue your trusted commandos from the clutches of the evil general plastero. Enjoy tense commando action in oe of 14 different missions as sarge rolls, dives and climbs through dangerous enemy environments. Good Luck, Soldier!','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Oct 30, 2000','T','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/257232-army-men-sarges-heroes');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1611,'South Park: Chef''s Luv Shack','All your favorite South park characters are waiting for you at Chefs Luv Shack. Spreading the hot buttered game lovin with dozens of crazy mini-games. Testing your South park knowledge with outrageous trivia questions. And telling it like it is with insane sound-bites! Spread the luv!','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Oct 31, 1999','M','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/198716-south-park-chefs-luv-shack');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1612,'NFL Blitz 2000','Its back and its better than ever! NFL Blitz 2000 adds new offensive and defensive plays, realistic weather conditions, new stadiums and a Tournament mode! Customize offensive and defensive plays to your liking. Call audibles at the line of scrimmage. Youve got control now! Passing made easy with new "Blitz Passing" for one-touch long bombs! "ON-FIRE" mode gives super power performance to your players! With non-stop action and a "pick-it-up-and-play" learning curve, NFL BLITZ 2000 is THE game for every football fan!','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Aug 31, 1999','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/198144-nfl-blitz-2000');
