INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1628,'Gunbird 2','Straight from the hit arcade game, Gunbird 2 is the most intense test of coordination and skill. This action shooters features 7 characters on a quest for the magical ingredients to produce the All-Purpose Medicine. On a journey to see the wise medicine master, you are intercepted by a rowdy band of pirates. Now, maneuver through insane levels of enemy fire to pick up power-ups and other weapons and be the first to recover your stolen bounty and unlock the secret of the medicine master.','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Nov 17, 2000','T','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/197507-gunbird-2');
