INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1671,'Wetrix+','A rainstorm so fierce, it will keep you from leaving your home for the next six months. Wetrix just might be the most addictive puzzle game of all time. Using randomly shaped 3D blocks as they fall from the sky, you must create a series of lakes and dams before the heavy rains appear. Because if the water drains, you lose! Sound simple? Well, mix in a few natural disasters and bomb attacks, and suddenly you need to muster all your strategy and skill to combat natures fury!','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Dec 31, 1999','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/199294-wetrix');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1672,'Midway''s Greatest Arcade Hits Volume 1','Six arcade classics are back for one low price, available only on the Sega Dreamcast™. Go back to 1982 again and save the humans once more from the evil Robotrons. Get in the cockpit of your spacecraft and take down the alien invaders in Defender and Defender II. Rid the sink of scum and filth in another game of Bubbles. Mine the reaches of outer space and defend your ship against the evil Sinistar. Or mount your winged bird of prey and take over the laval pits in a game of Joust.','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Jun 27, 2000','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/257231-midways-greatest-arcade-hits-volume-1');
