INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1867,'Slave Zero','Its 500 years in the future. Man and machine are virtually one and the greatest megacity in the world is locked in a brutal war. You are the ultimate saboteur and part of an elite fighting force. Your mission: Steal the largest, most sophisticated biomechanical attack weapon ever designed... and kick some serious ass!','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Oct 31, 1999','T','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/198671-slave-zero');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1868,'Sega Rally Championship 2','The greatest rally game in the arcades is now available in your own home. With the addition of a 10 Year Championship and gruelling driving conditions through mud, deserts, blizzard, night time and many more. Choose from a multitude of world famous rally cars on 17 challenging courses. Upload your best times to the internet or view the high score tables.','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Oct 31, 1999','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/198573-sega-rally-championship-2');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1869,'Midway''s Greatest Arcade Hits Volume 2','Midways Greatest Arcade Hits Volume 2 is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Digital Eclipse and published by Midway, which was released in 2001.','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Nov 15, 2001','T','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/577792-midways-greatest-arcade-hits-volume-2');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1870,'Toy Commander','Be nice to your toys! Its all-out war as neglected old-time toys rebel against the shiny new generation for the title of Toy Commander. Not your average fun and games! -Full immersion in an awesome 3D interactive environment -Choose from 35 different vehicles -50 missions with multiple objectives -Deathmatch mode with 3 distinct ways to play -Up to four-players screen action','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Sep 30, 1999','E','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/199093-toy-commander');
INSERT INTO "INFO" VALUES(1871,'Space Channel 5','Get into the groove with Ulala, space goddess extraordinaire and TV diva, out-dance those evil but funky invading aliens, rescue their wacky dancing hostages, and get her TV ratings to soar! "Space Channel 5" merges adventure and music action with a hip leading lady who will groove the hearts of gamers of all ages. "Space Channel 5" has mesmerizing gameplay, with characters and visuals so unique, why resist? The rhythms gonna get ya!','Dreamcast','Dreamcast','Jun  4, 2000','T','http://www.gamefaqs.com/dreamcast/256048-space-channel-5');
